{"hash":"FF4502E53705EF50B7D546409B2108C4","rights":"CC BY","creator":"batch","uri":"http://learningandyearning.com/herb-infused-oil","time":"2016-11-23","title":"You use herbs everyday. They are wonderful for adding flavor to our foods, and can also have great value as home medicine. Making medicinal teas is one way to consume herbs but sometimes an herb is needed externally to relieve itch, soothe a rash, or provide pain relief.  By steeping herbs in oil many of its chemical components can be extracted and preserved for future use in healing salves and balms."}